            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">You will also learn <mark>how to reduce the code complexity from one Big-O level to another level</mark>, an important skill to impress the interviewer.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
